cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically object detection and pose estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of a PnP algorithm for pose estimation could also place it under cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the focus on real-time processing suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics).
